Mix @flour{270%g}, @oil{10%g}, @salt{1tsp} and @water{160%ml}. Knead well and let rest for at least ~{1%h}.

Form balls of 45 g each and roll out, the recipe should yield 10 parathas. 
Brush with oil, butter or ghee. Sprinkle some flour on top and then roll into a tube. 

Roll tube from both sides, smash down and let rest for ~{30%min}.

Roll out and bake on hot pan.